<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1524401-is-this-book-actually-related-to-the-other">Is this book actually related to the other two listed in the &quot;series&quot; -- Summer of Night and Winter Haunting? I ask because although it&#39;s listed as part of the series, it doesn&#39;t seem to have anything to do with the other two books.</a>
</div>
