<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Mike O&apos; Rourke, the priest mentioned in this novel, is one of the main characters from Summer of Night, but all grown up.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Mike O' Rourke, the priest mentioned in this novel, is one of the main characters from Summer of Night, but all grown up.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
