    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_749540414" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/749540414" />
    <a title="Carol" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7668522-carol"><img alt="Carol" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1546364878p2/7668522.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/749540414?book_show_action=true">Oct 25, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Carol" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Carol" href="/user/show/7668522-carol">Carol</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781250009852" href="/book/show/13538899-children-of-the-night">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7668522-carol?shelf=horror">horror</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7668522-carol?shelf=vampires">vampires</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7668522-carol?shelf=read-2014">read-2014</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer749540414" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer748389346341014157">Be forewarned that <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/11290.Children_of_the_Night' title='Children of the Night by Dan Simmons' rel='nofollow noopener'>Children of the Night</a> starts out with a brutally realistic description of post Communist Romania and the inhumane treatment of thousands of babies that is quite disturbing. Once beyond that, beware of the sections interspersed throughout the book written with the voice of &quot;Vlad the Impaler&quot; (the original Dracula) as they are gruesome, gory and scary as <i>hell</i>. A few parts of the book, including the ending, was a bit <i>James Bondish</i>, but overall, a fast-moving and entertaining read</span>
  <span id="freeText748389346341014157" style="display:none">Be forewarned that <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/11290.Children_of_the_Night" title="Children of the Night by Dan Simmons" rel="nofollow noopener">Children of the Night</a> starts out with a brutally realistic description of post Communist Romania and the inhumane treatment of thousands of babies that is quite disturbing. Once beyond that, beware of the sections interspersed throughout the book written with the voice of "Vlad the Impaler" (the original Dracula) as they are gruesome, gory and scary as <i>hell</i>. A few parts of the book, including the ending, was a bit <i>James Bondish</i>, but overall, a fast-moving and entertaining read with an important scientific twist. <p>As a new fan of Dan Simmons, <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/3974.The_Terror" title="The Terror by Dan Simmons" rel="nofollow noopener">The Terror</a> is next!</p></span>
  <a data-text-id="748389346341014157" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


