<span id="freeTextContainer12713460575807846893">The vampire myth is updated to the 1990&apos;s in this horror novel. A female doctor goes to Romania and adopts one of the lost children of the communist regime. It seems like the baby is allergic to sunlight, and can&apos;t eat regular food, but somehow blood makes it stronger, and cures all of its illnesses. <br/><br/>The doctor believes the baby might lead to the cure for AIDS, while others believe...darker theories. They both might be right.</span>
